data.name: Label2.Text
data.value:
In this game your task is to nurture your dragon of choice. You must feed the dragon for as long as possible without letting it get sick or die. You must make the dragon strong and proud!
Here's how it works: --> You start off with an egg that you must keep warm without it overheating or becoming too cold for the dragon to grow out of
--> After the egg hatches, you must care for the baby dragon up until it reaches its adult cycle. Once it reaches its adult cycle you are challenged to keep the dragon alive as long as possible. There will be a timer in the corner of the screen that records how long you are caring for the dragon.
--> There will be 3 bars on the lower part of the screen that will determine the health and emotion of the dragon. Your goal is to keep the dragon healthy and prevent it from getting angry, which can be caused by not feeding the dragon.
--> If you don't feed the dragon the dragon dies, and the game will be over.
Good Luck!
